Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.29,0:00:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是… 那陔子真正的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.48,0:00:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎吧！直到银河的尽头!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧… 阿尔特…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:31.36,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 敌主炮发射!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.46,0:00:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.37,0:00:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能再由你们任意摆布了\N{\fs10}\N{\r}兰花也是，Vajra也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross Quarter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.05,0:01:05.48,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 太慢了啊，奥茨玛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.61,0:01:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 抱歉，有点事耽搁了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.39,0:01:13.39,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 奥茨玛少校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 笨蛋，要叫队长，Skull-3
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skull-3… 队长!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了\N{\fs10}\N{\r}为了打破Galaxy的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及在背后的格蕾斯·奥康纳\N{\fs10}\N{\r}和她的同伙的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.94,0:01:34.29,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你说Galaxy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.64,0:01:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的，我们被利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.29,0:01:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被他们的阴谋和他们的支持者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么根据说那样的胡话!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,证据的话，证据的话我有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:50.42,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Skull-4的IFF
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我… 看到了\N{\fs10}\N{\r}那家伙的原形
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是兰花\N{\fs10}\N{\r}攻击那个假象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:11.82,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.76,0:02:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:31.53,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- Battle Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不是应该被Vajra干掉了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三岛总统阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍后请您详细解释\N{\fs10}\N{\r}也包括格拉斯总统的暗杀事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:45.35,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(197,420)}- 暗杀?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(373,420)}总统不是被Vajra杀死的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}- 怎么可能，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧，雷昂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:55.38,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 被识破了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.29,0:02:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 意外地很能干呢，那些少年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:03:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H6464FF&}没关系\N{\fs10}\N{\r}也只有现在能让他们做场美梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长，Battle Galaxy中的大量热源\N{\fs10}\N{\r}发射出来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:13.06,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是… Ghost V9！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你说V9?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 好快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:32.30,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- Skull-3呼叫Skull-4，阿尔特前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 听到的话就快回话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卢卡，柯岚上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:41.02,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 来，接住了，阿尔特，你的机体！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skull-4呼叫Battle Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说，雪露\N{\fs10}\N{\r}这次一定把兰花救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，把你的力量借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用你的歌把那家伙唤醒吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:59.80,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 歌?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:03:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是啊，你的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了哦，大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候，听到了你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的… 内心的呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.33,Default italize,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会思考的是鲜花\N{\fs10}\N{\r}会思考的成不了鲜花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要，跟随着感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要，飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全机，上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:01.43,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- “突击 Love Heart!”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔，给我力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙，尤哈妮，佩特洛\N{\fs10}\N{\r}现在就解除你们的枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去，曾让Macross City\N{\fs10}\N{\r}陷入恐怖深渊的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,JUDAH系统，释放！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰花，听到了吗?\N{\fs10}\N{\r}我的声音，雪露的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:17.33,Default italize,,0000,0000,0000,,醒过来吧，兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌声，取回你真正的歌声吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:29.74,Default italize,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，连接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:17.12,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 强烈的Fold波，史无前例的级别
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:32.50,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- Fold Wave，急速展开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 星系全域正在构造网络结构！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:38.63,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 队长，Vajra的行动…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Galaxy混蛋，到底干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，感觉到了… 感觉到了啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FE00&}这是星座，这是银河
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Little Queen什么的，已经没用了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(269,460)}我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(375,460)\c&H6464FF&}得到了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好了，虫子们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:08:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在已经将全宇宙掌握在手中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连Protoculture都对这力量\N{\fs10}\N{\r}感到害怕，向往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用Vajra的力量\N{\fs10}\N{\r}最终神化成为这种姿态的超时空生命体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:19.27,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这声音… 格蕾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这么巨大…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.56,0:08:31.85,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不起作用?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是… 次元断层
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对直接和Quee连接的我们来说\N{\fs10}\N{\r}歌已经毫无意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来，膜拜吧!\N{\fs10}\N{\r}与支配命运的神等同的我们的力量!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧，Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼，我的耳，我的手足\N{\fs10}\N{\r}与那强韧的利爪一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H6464FF&}好好记住，我们的力量吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，兰花，阿尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经… 不行了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好，兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中弹的缘故，总算逃脱了他们的支配
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧，歌唱吧，兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤，愤怒，喜悦\N{\fs10}\N{\r}把你所有的心情，融入歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，这次一定要阻止这场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们兄妹的救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这歌声是… 兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌声将Vajra…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于兰花·李的歌声\N{\fs10}\N{\r}Vajra的攻击停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:17.88,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么，不是背叛到敌方去了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，在与Vajra女王的Fold波相抗衡\N{\fs10}\N{\r}范围不断扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站起来，雪露小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样，我的工作已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有留下，什么都…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请回想起来，雪露小姐\N{\fs10}\N{\r}因为有雪露小姐在，我才能起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是因为有雪露小姐的力量\N{\fs10}\N{\r}阿尔特才能飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:09.58,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,420)}雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H6464FF&\pos(350,419)}阿尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,460)}你说过吧，决不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，所以来吧，雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是，你们是… 我的双翼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，再一次飞翔吧，雪露小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向此战场上的所有士兵通告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra并不是我们真正的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy和篡夺Vajra女王的格蕾斯·奥康纳\N{\fs10}\N{\r}才是我们真正的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以羽翼为骄傲的人啊\N{\fs10}\N{\r}与我们一同前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,声波坐标确认
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pin-Point Barrier集中在主炮前端
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼，无谓的挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:34.20,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 朝向Island 1的直击过来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么！?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被Vajra… 保护了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢，大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:09.53,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传达到了吗\N{\fs10}\N{\r}歌声，我和雪露小姐的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra也有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，和我们很不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么人类全都分散着各自\N{\fs10}\N{\r}做着不同的事，它们无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以Vajra想从难以理解的人类里\N{\fs10}\N{\r}把可以用Fold波沟通的我救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，在感觉到和我不同的\N{\fs10}\N{\r}雪露小姐的歌声后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解到我们每个人都是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不把心意好好传达的话\N{\fs10}\N{\r}就无法彼此理解的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们终于明白了这点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:15:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家，相互拥抱吧\N{\fs10}\N{\r}直到银河的尽头!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女王的协议无法传输?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是歌的力量吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,断层护盾再次展开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样才能突破呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通道… Vajra在断层中打开了通道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全军，跟着Vajra前进!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主炮损伤，无法射击！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在，Macross Attack！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上吧，阿尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:18.63,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们的未来！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们的希望！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔特，这个交给你了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不明白吗?\N{\fs10}\N{\r}这才是人类进化的终极姿态啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么进化啊\N{\fs10}\N{\r}明明只是让Vajra牺牲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:59.63,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我来掩护你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(288,460)}- 布雷拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(371,460)\c&HFFFFFF&}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:03.67,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 阿尔特，瞄准女王的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 脑袋?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra的心不在脑袋上，而是在肚子里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra是在肚子中歌唱的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些臭虫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你们接触后，终于理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:24.72,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不论走到哪里，人都是单独的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H6464FF&}- 所以我们要…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FE00&\pos(242,460)}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(361,460)}正是因为一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才会爱上某个人啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:55.26,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这就是Vajra的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:21:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐，如果说Vajra是\N{\fs10}\N{\r}不需要交流的物种的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这歌… 曾作为什么的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:07.59,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“求爱之歌”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:13.55,Default italize,,0000,0000,0000,,求爱?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra在数万年中\N{\fs10}\N{\r}不，数亿年一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与别的银河中所居住的群族相遇\N{\fs10}\N{\r}为了求偶而歌唱的求爱之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AIMO AIMO\N{\fs10}\N{\r}就是 “亲爱的  亲爱的”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.19,0:21:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪露小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.38,0:22:13.15,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,- 阿尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.38,0:22:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H6464FF&}- 阿尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.53,0:22:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪露与兰花所带来的\N{\fs10}\N{\r}真正的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.37,0:22:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋正在飞翔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.48,0:22:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个，雪露小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.21,0:23:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会输的\N{\fs10}\N{\r}歌也好，恋爱也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受你的挑战哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.34,0:23:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪露小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.09,0:23:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在，才开始呢
